    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint retains its original showroom luster with no scratches or dents, and the interior is pristine, featuring leather that looks and smells like new. Mechanically, the car is flawless; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Every electronic feature and safety system functions perfectly, and the full service history confirms that no expense has been spared in its upkeep. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from one on a new car lot.",
