      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior does show its age with some visible scratches, small dings, and faded paint on the hood. The interior is clean but has some wear on the driver's seat and a few stains on the carpet. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the price tag of a newer model.",
